      "zoneName": "us-east-1a",
      "zoneState": {
        "available": true
      },
      "hosts": null
    },
    {
      "zoneName": "us-east-1b",
      "zoneState": {
        "available": false
      },
      "hosts": null
    }
    // ... more zones
  ]
}
```

The program should define the necessary structs to correctly unmarshal the JSON response and include a method to extract the names of the available zones (zones where `available` is `true`).

